videos.description: Baylor's Jared Butler spins in the lane and misses a wild shot off the backboard, but Mark Vital is there to clean up with the putback dunk.
videos.headline: Baylor's Vital flushes putback slam

videos.description: MaCio Teague and Freddie Gillespie run the pick-and-roll to perfection as Teague hits a cutting Gillespie for the and-1 score.

videos.description: Jared Butler has the ball on a string as he uses a series of crossovers to leave his defender in the dust en route to an easy layup.
